{
  "stem": "19242.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 504.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were the first one really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were selling-- we were the first one to put electricity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was 1937.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, after that time, after that time we didn't have electricity, and the town didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were selling it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, we were selling it in the store to people that wanted it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that time, there was lamps, you know, gasoline lamps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not indoor plumbing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No indoor water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember I used to carry the water on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, you go to the well, and-- and then you have barrels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, you dump the water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I was young and didn't mind to do that though.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not for my older brother or my daughter because--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only for me that they had one-- a governess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She just-- all what she did is took care of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was her job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, most of the time, my mother was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, I mean, she didn't-- in the kitchen, she didn't-- she was cleaning and taking care of me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's about all she did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember she used to come even-- even she got married, she didn't have no children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She used to come and check up on me, see how I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But otherwise-- well, she helped me out during the war a little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But always she couldn't do I suppose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Someone else who went [INAUDIBLE] really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very observant.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like Shabbos well, Shabbos-- well, you remember, like, we had that store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Shabbos in-- like the night before, and he says, close the store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to klopf at the stechen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had to close the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
